urg Masters \u2013 Singles|*]]\n| style=\"background:#F5F5F5;\" | Nadal[[2007 Italian Open \u2013 Men's Singles|*]]\n| style=\"background:#5F5F5;\" | Djokovic[[2007 Rogers Masters \u2013 Singles|*]]\n| style=\"background:#F5F5F5;\" | Federer[[2007 Western & Southern Financial Group Masters \u2013 Singles|*]]\n| style=\"background:#5F5F5;\" | Nalbandian[[2007 Mutua Madrilena Masters Madrid \u2013 Singles|*]]\n| style=\"background:#F5F5F5;\" | Nalbandian[[2007 BNP Paribas Masters \u2013 Singles|*]]\n| style=\"background:#FFFFE6;\" | Federer[[2007 Tennis Masters Cup \u2013 Singles|*]]\n| style=\"background:#f5f5f5; color:#ccc;\u201c|{{sort|zz|Not held}}\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|'''[[2006 ATP Tour|2006]]'''\n| style=\"background:#E6F2FF;\" | Federer[[2006 Australian Open \u2013 Men's Singles|*]]\n| style=\"background:#f9f0eb;\" | Nadal[[2006 French Open \u2013 Men's Singles|*]]\n| style=\"background:#F2FFE6;\" | Federer[[2006 Wimbledon Championships \u2013 Men's Singles|*]]\n| style=\"background:#E6F2FF;\" | Federer[[2006 US Open \u2013 Men's Singles|*]]\n| style=\"background:#F5F5F5;\" | Federer[[2006 Indian Wells Masters - Men's Singles|*]]\n| style=\"background:#5F5F5;\" | Federer[[2006 Miami Masters - Men's Singles|*]]\n| style=\"background:#F5F5F5;\" | Nadal[[2006 Monte Carlo Masters \u2013 Singles|*]]\n| style=\"background:#5F5F5;\" | [[Tommy Robredo|Robredo]][[2006 Hamburg Masters \u2013 Singles|*]]\n| style=\"background:#F5F5F5;\" | Nadal[[2006 Italian Open \u2013 Men's Singles|*]]\n| style=\"background:#5F5F5;\" | Federer[[2006 Rogers Masters \u2013 Singles|*]]\n| style=\"background:#F5F5F5;\" | Roddick[[2006 Western & Southern Financial Group Masters \u2013 Singles|*]]\n| style=\"background:#5F5F5;\" | Federer[[2006 Mutua Madrilena Masters Madrid \u2013 Singles|*]]\n| style=\"background:#F5F5F5;\" | [[Nikolay Davydenko|Davydenko]][[2006 BNP Paribas Masters \u2013 Singles|*]]\n| style=\"background:#FFFFE6;\" | Federer[[2006 Tennis Masters Cup \u2013 